<div id="<%= dom_id(profile, :training_block_generation) %>">
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/5 p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
    <span class="mt-0.5 h-5 w-5 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-400 border-t-transparent animate-spin"></span>
    <div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-200">Building your training plan…</div>
      <div class="text-xs text-slate-300 mt-1">This usually takes 1–3 minutes because the coach is generating a full multi-week block.</div>
      <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">You can keep this tab open. If the live update misses, this page will refresh automatically to check for the finished plan.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
